Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife. In this volume, Ichigo regains his powers and learns a startling truth about himself.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 54
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Was a group called the Seven Moons responsible for the death of Ritsuka’s brother?
Title: LOVELESS, VOL. 10
Author: Yun Kouga

Description: Isn’t being a kid hard enough? For this group, who are also part bird, nothing comes easy.
Title: MAXIMUM RIDE, VOL. 6
Author: James Patterson

Description: Staz is a vampire obsessed with Japanese culture. When a young Japanese girl he befriends suddenly dies, Staz vows to restore her, especially since it will give him a chance to walk among humans.
Title: BLOOD LAD, VOL. 1
Author: Yuuki Kodama

Description: Two female high school students, Mariko Kumakura and Akko Oohashi, have become a couple. Will they take it public?
Title: GIRL FRIENDS: THE COMPLETE COLLECTION, VOL. 2
Author: Morinaga Milk

Description: A social agency in Italy is taking in young girl and turning them into assassins. Meet their latest: Henrietta, who comes equipped with cybernetic technology.
Title: GUNSLINGER GIRL, OMNIBUS VOL. 6
Author: Yu Aida

Description: Naruto and his allies battle an army of undead ninjas and an unexpected resurrection throws them all for a loop.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 59
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: This is not your typical wonderland: Peter is a man with rabbit ears and Elliott March, the Mad Hatter’s enforcer, is a mafia hitman. How will Alice survive?
Title: ALICE IN THE COUNTRY OF HEARTS: MY FANATIC RABBIT, VOL. 1
Author: Quinrose

Description: Ritsuka is heartbroken over his brother’s death, but will the insight that Soubi, a mysterious, handsome college student, has make things any better?
Title: LOVELESS: 2-IN-1, VOL. 2
Author: Yun Kouga

Description: Are the magical dreams of Madoka Kaname suddenly becoming a reality?
Title: PUELLA MAGI MADOKA MAGICA, VOL. 3
Author: Magica Quartet
